22:47.540 --> 22:48.932
[LAUGHS] Ireland, baby!

22:48.976 --> 22:50.238
NARRATOR: An all new season.

22:50.281 --> 22:52.414
Do you mind if I go sample
some of your jellies?

22:52.458 --> 22:54.111
No, help yourself.Delightful.

22:54.808 --> 22:56.331
[GAGGING]

22:56.375 --> 22:57.637
A banquet...What?

22:57.680 --> 22:58.725
[GAGGING]Ew.

