...of humiliation...[ALL EXCLAIMING]

23:01.292 --> 23:02.381
...and murder.Wait, what?

23:02.424 --> 23:04.121
[ALL SCREAMING]

23:04.165 --> 23:06.646
All right. This is why
Irish people hate Americans.

23:06.689 --> 23:10.650
[NARRATOR READING]

23:10.693 --> 23:13.392
[SHEEP BLEATING]

23:14.784 --> 23:15.829
No one has seen
a stolen food truck, would ya?

23:15.872 --> 23:17.961
Um... no.

23:18.005 --> 23:19.920
Someone stole a truck.
Broad daylight.

23:19.963 --> 23:21.400
MAN: Put your seatbelt on.Seatbelt?

23:21.443 --> 23:23.880
Put your seatbelt on
or we're not leaving.Jeez!

23:23.924 --> 23:25.708
MAN: Your good thieves.
Best in town.

23:25.752 --> 23:26.796
Thank you.

23:26.840 --> 23:27.971
It is a small town.

23:29.233 --> 23:32.106
It is hard to be a warrior
with dignity.

23:32.149 --> 23:43.422
[SCREAMS] [COUGHS]

23:44.074 --> 23:45.249
Brace yourselves.

23:45.293 --> 23:46.729
Give me your best arguments.Sure.

23:46.773 --> 23:48.252
WOMAN: Pop culture
is a religion.

23:48.296 --> 23:49.558
Fire. [CHUCKLES]

23:49.602 --> 23:51.734
You're in an era
where we worship celebrity.

23:51.778 --> 23:52.866
Oh, and also...

23:52.909 --> 23:54.215
Susie, shh!

23:54.258 --> 23:56.435
I don't listen to people,
I listen to God.

23:56.478 --> 23:57.871
It's constitutionally
guaranteed.

23:59.699 --> 24:01.396
Oh, terrible.

24:01.440 --> 24:03.529
I'm here
to present the future.

24:03.572 --> 24:05.922
I posted that black square,
I deleted that black square,

24:05.966 --> 24:07.097
I reposted the black square,

24:07.141 --> 24:08.447
and then I redeleted
the black square.
